"YUV 4:4:4 increases chroma sample load and usually needs more bitrate or lower FPS to stay clean." = "YUV 4:4:4 会明显增加色度采样负载，通常需要更高码率或更低帧率才能保持干净画质。";
"Pixel throughput is above 1.0 Gpix/s, so encode/decode/render timing becomes very sensitive." = "像素吞吐已超过 1.0 Gpix/s，编码、解码和渲染链路的时序会变得非常敏感。";
